/RZSFKACR",{"type":179,"bibl":180},"discussion",[89],{"editor":182,"principal":185,"contributors":186,"change":198},{"_":183,"ref":184},"Jonathan Prag","#JP",{"_":183,"ref":184},[187,190,194],{"_":183,"xml:id":188,"ref":189},"JP","http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537",{"_":191,"xml:id":192,"ref":193},"James Cummings","JCu","http://orcid.org/0000-0002-6686-3728",{"_":195,"xml:id":196,"ref":197},"Simona Stoyanova","SS","https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569",{"_":199,"when":200,"who":184},"Jonathan Prag revised from publications","2025-12-04",[],[203,204,205,206,207,208,209],"Gualtherus, 1624 [1625], Siciliæ obiacentium insular. et Bruttiorum antiquæ tabulæ, cum animadversionib","Castelli, 1769, Siciliae et objacentium insularum veterum inscriptionum nova collectio","Castelli, 1784, Siciliae et objacentium insularum veterum inscriptionum nova collectio prolegomenis et notis illustrata, et iterum cum emendationibus, & auctariis evulgata","Mommsen, 1883, CIL","Bivona, 2000, La documentazione epigrafica latina in area elima","Manganaro, 1987, Tacfarinas e la Sicilia (ovvero L. Apronius e il santuario ericino","Manganaro, 1988, La Sicilia da Sesto Pompeo a Diocleziano",[211,212,213,214,215,216,217],"ZP8DE8KS","SPTB56H3","7PSFHSUH","GQN8UZSI","94ICR94M","RVZG5HIX","RZSFKACR",[219,220,221,27,32,36,222,223,224,225,223,226,103],"isic000539","fragment of latin inscription on a marble arch",{"_":5},"eryx","erice","sicilia","sicily","latin",[],{"title":229,"body":230,"divs":231,"editions":256,"images":266,"handnote":267},"ISic000539. Fragment of Latin inscription on a marble arch","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Lucius · Seius · Luci · filius · Aemila tribu Fir\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Lucius\">L(ucius)\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Seius\">Seius\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Luci\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Luci\">L(uci)\u003C/span>\u003C/span> · f(ilius) · Aem(ila) (\u003Cem>scil.\u003C/em> tribu) \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Fir\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Fir\">Fir\u003C/span>\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>P · pec [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] inpen[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Lucius · Seius · Luci · filius · Aemila tribu Fir\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Lucius\">L\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Seius\">SEIUS\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Luci\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Luci\">L\u003C/span>\u003C/span>·F·AEM(\u003Cem>scil.\u003C/em> TRIBU)\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Fir\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Fir\">FIR\u003C/span>\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>P·PEC[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]INPEN[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text of CIL, after Gualtherus and Cordici\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan>Gualtherus: FIR omitted, lacuna marked; FIR recorded by Ventimiglia (so Mommsen); Cordici: I·PCC, later deleted\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: \u003Cspan>Cordici: EFFE·INPEN, later deleted\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Manganaro and Mommsen both noted that the name L.Seius also appears on coins of Panhormus as proconsul of Sicily, in the late Augustan period, and identification with the L. Seius here, making a dedication at Erice, would be attractive, but far from certain. The consul of 18 CE seems less likely, as his cognomen Tubero does not seem to align with the traces variously recorded at the end of line 1 in the antiquarian tradition. P.PEC might be p(osuit) pec(unia). \u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] no. 156 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Castelli 1769 cl. 7, no. 24 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Castelli 1784 cl. 7, no. 25 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Mommsen 1883 \u003Ca href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">7259\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1987 583 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001833\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001833\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1988 22 n.83 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bivona 2000 155 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002135\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002135\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[232,235,238,241,244,247,250,253],{"id":233,"html":234},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumb